{"type":"message","id":"f76287da","parentId":"3f175a8b","timestamp":"2026-06-06T03:10:28.781Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"sorftime MCP 服务器完全正常。API 端点是 `https://mcp.sorftime.com/`，不是之前尝试的 `api.sorftime.com`。MCP 服务器本身运行良好。\n\n用户说\"这个mcp工具这么不稳定吗\"，可能是指之前用 sorftime MCP 时遇到了问题。让我告诉用户 MCP 服务器本身是正常的，并询问具体遇到了什么问题。","thinkingSignature":"cbad8d5c8512938db41441824f8a0b85b7d81e38a98945d402a26c019d6a29bf"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n检查结果：\n\n**sorftime MCP 服务器本身运行正常** ✅\n- API 端点：`https://mcp.sorftime.com/`（配置在 `workspace-tts/config/mcporter.json`）\n- `get_time` 工具测试：正常返回 `2026-06-06 11:10:24`\n- 工具列表：正常返回 40+ 个可用工具\n\n你说的不稳定具体是指什么情况？\n- 某个特定工具调用报错？\n- 连接超时？\n- 额度用完？\n\n可以告诉我具体哪次操作出了问题，我来查日志看看原因。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":222,"output":199,"cacheRead":118720,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":119141,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780715424403,"responseId":"0672c2a11992aeacfc78360dd4cfb36f"}}
