{"type":"message","id":"dde216ff","parentId":"d49d4a63","timestamp":"2026-06-06T10:10:00.939Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying that Sorftime MCP doesn't support Thailand (TH) market. Let me look at the tools available to confirm - from the tool list I got earlier, I can see Shopee sites support: VN, ID, SG, TH, MY, TW, PH, BR. And TikTok sites support: US, MY, PH, VN, TH, ID, GB, JP.\n\nSo TH should be supported for Shopee and TikTok at least. But maybe the user is referring to a specific tool or data source that doesn't support TH. Let me check what the SOP says about this.\n\n\nLooking at the user's memory, the core strategy is \"趋势黑马拦截 + 三级漏斗验证 + 1688利润终选\" for Vietnam and Thailand markets, so TH is definitely part of the target. But the user is saying Sorftime MCP doesn't support Thailand, which seems contradictory since the tool list shows TH as available for Shopee and TikTok. Maybe they're referring to a specific API endpoint or data source within Sorftime that lacks TH support, or perhaps the issue is with how certain tools are configured for that market.\n","thinkingSignature":"8e8606fe9c72173098fffc59506b8da660ce2477a571871fbd91c238300f3baf"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n确认一下，从刚才拿到的工具列表看：\n\n**Shopee 支持 TH** ✅  \n站点枚举：`VN, ID, SG, TH, MY, TW, PH, BR`\n\n**TikTok 支持 TH** ✅  \n站点枚举：`US, MY, PH, VN, TH, ID, GB, JP`\n\n**Amazon 不支持 TH** ❌  \n站点枚举：`US, GB, DE, FR, IN, CA, JP, ES, IT, MX, AE, AU, BR, SA`\n\n---\n\n你是说哪个工具报错？是 `shopee_category_request` 还是 `tiktok_*` 还是别的？可以给我看看具体的错误信息吗？"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":116543,"output":365,"cacheRead":1212,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":118120,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780740584802,"responseId":"067324e91cd33b31a699d8b413ac63e5"}}
