{"type":"message","id":"9c595e72","parentId":"0ea01c66","timestamp":"2026-06-06T10:14:44.337Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is saying that sorftime MCP doesn't support Thailand (TH) market. They want to use Shopee data instead to get Thailand market data.\n\nLooking at the sorftime MCP tools I got earlier, the Shopee tools support TH site (site: \"204:TH\"). So maybe the user is referring to TikTok not supporting Thailand, but they want to use Shopee as an alternative data source.\n\nLet me clarify - the user said \"sorftime mcp不支持 th ❌ 泰国市场\" and \"可以用shopee的数据看\" - so they want to look at Thailand market using Shopee data through sorftime MCP.\n\nThe sorftime MCP has `shopee_product_search` and `shopee_category_request` tools that support TH (site: \"204:TH\"). Let me confirm this is what they need.\n\nActually, I should ask them to clarify what specifically they want to do - are they looking for:\n1. Thailand TikTok trending products?\n2. Thailand Shopee products?\n3. Something else?\n\nOr maybe they're saying the tiktok_category_name_search tool doesn't support TH, but Shopee does support TH. Let me just ask for clarification on what they need.\n","thinkingSignature":"60127060ba026916410a667a37992c64dbeab6fcddf13b12698b489aeb6d9148"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\n明白，Sorftime 的 TikTok 相关工具不支持泰国站点。但 **Shopee 工具支持泰国（site: 204:TH）**。\n\n你具体想查什么？\n\n1. **泰国 Shopee 类目爆品** - 用 `shopee_category_request` 查指定类目下的 Best Seller\n2. **泰国 Shopee 关键词搜索** - 用 `shopee_product_search` 搜索产品\n3. **泰国 Shopee 商品详情/趋势** - 用 `shopee_product_trend` 查历史趋势\n\n告诉我你要查什么，我帮你调对应的工具。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":523,"output":364,"cacheRead":117374,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":118261,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780740874889,"responseId":"0673260bd3f914d99b8e80ff09b9b951"}}
